Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今之泥坑用山寨廠cmos<br />\n產能低質素低<br />\n越影越多noise</blockquote><br />\n你幾時變左狙擊Nikon架？</blockquote><br />\nNikon唔用佢主子既Cmos佢嬲豬<br />\n雖然佢以為Nikon要屈服用Sony cmos個陣佢就笑鳩Nikon比競爭對手揸住春袋<br />\n龍門任佢擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢點解釋山寨廠出到4750 萬像BSI<br />\nSony有1億像Sensor都只能夠用4500萬像舊Sensor?<br />\n<br />\n主子無左大客會連創新能力都無左？<br />\n定真係順手「借」用Nikon技術呀</blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇左條YouTube d850 vs a7riii<br />\n ISO 100 d850 wins a7riii <br />\nlooks even better at ISO64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f110f3116202f3595b41164a87a93af9186baf2","tid":462021,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今之泥坑用山寨廠cmos<br />\n產能低質素低<br />\n越影越多noise</blockquote><br />\n你幾時變左狙擊Nikon架？</blockquote><br />\nNikon唔用佢主子既Cmos佢嬲豬<br />\n雖然佢以為Nikon要屈服用Sony cmos個陣佢就笑鳩Nikon比競爭對手揸住春袋<br />\n龍門任佢擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢點解釋山寨廠出到4750 萬像BSI<br />\nSony有1億像Sensor都只能夠用4500萬像舊Sensor?<br />\n<br />\n主子無左大客會連創新能力都無左？<br />\n定真係順手「借」用Nikon技術呀</blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇左條YouTube d850 vs a7riii<br />\n ISO 100 d850 wins a7riii <br />\nlooks even better at ISO64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估DXO A7RIII應該過100分"},{"pid":"63d33b2def27fed603040c36df3f2f501c8c8800","tid":462021,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今之泥坑用山寨廠cmos<br />\n產能低質素低<br />\n越影越多noise</blockquote><br />\n你幾時變左狙擊Nikon架？</blockquote><br />\nNikon唔用佢主子既Cmos佢嬲豬<br />\n雖然佢以為Nikon要屈服用Sony cmos個陣佢就笑鳩Nikon比競爭對手揸住春袋<br />\n龍門任佢擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢點解釋山寨廠出到4750 萬像BSI<br />\nSony有1億像Sensor都只能夠用4500萬像舊Sensor?<br />\n<br />\n主子無左大客會連創新能力都無左？<br />\n定真係順手「借」用Nikon技術呀</blockquote><br />\n啱啱睇左條YouTube d850 vs a7riii<br />\n ISO 100 d850 wins a7riii <br />\nlooks even better at ISO64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSony 其實有既係技術同產能<br />\n但cmos 設計同軟件不嬲都弱<br />\n<br />\n好多nikon 同sony 用一期出既sensor, nikon DXO 既分會輕微高sony DD<br />\n因為有D高階用既sensor 係nikon 自己再設計同modify.<br />\n好似fuji 既X Trans咁"},{"pid":"50bc848e75052046e510ae0c8f4b59c9795efd6f","tid":462021,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13520c2e465ed5a0056e8ff26647572026b9b0d2","tid":462021,"uid":117044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:33:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af5d76f48b9825badd143b7bf0199015b0d41ed9","tid":462021,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aab4942fe2c77b4be035e7694881977739c9c07","tid":462021,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柒貓講到無野講，<br />\n就會話單反有反光板震震震，<br />\n震到構圖到歪埋，<br />\n難為佢自己差不多張張唔中焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢到而家都未指出其實D850係4570萬像素<br />\nA7RIII係4240萬像素<br />\n<br />\n比埋位佢入佢都唔識😂😂😂😂😂😂😂"},{"pid":"074ce314cdf1cf659807bdc6b4af0d5a40c0e1ad","tid":462021,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a8f93273fe0561932b0b2ba5d2b28053015b887","tid":462021,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"外國買相機，邊到信得過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}